data.meta_description:
33 likes, 0 comments - einsteinmed on May 3, 2024: "Scott Emmons, Ph.D., Elected to the NAS

Congratulations! Einstein’s Scott Emmons, Ph.D., who completed the first complete wiring diagram of an animal’s entire nervous system, has been elected to the National Academy of Sciences (NAS). Dr. Emmons is distinguished professor emeritus of genetics and in the Dominick P. Purpura Department of Neuroscience.

See Link in Bio to learn more. 

#science #research #biomedicalresearch #PhD #EinsteinMed #AlbertEinsteinCollegeofMedicine".
